npei Gotou—a legendary assassin tasked with executing her. Satoko tries to bribe Gotou into freeing her, but it proves unsuccessful. Out of options, Satoko makes a desperate gamble: under the pretense of love at first sight, she asks him to marry her.\n\nUnexpectedly, Gotou takes the bait and vows to protect her. As the couple escapes to freedom, Satoko struggles to keep up the ruse and make sense of the mysterious man she has eloped with.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]","streaming":[{"name":"Crunchyroll","url":"https://www.crunchyroll.com/"}],"type":"TV"},{"id":64254,"title":"Hyouken no Majutsushi ga Sekai wo Suberu II","title_english":"The Iceblade Sorcerer Shall Rule the World II","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1968/158143l.jpg","synopsis":"Second season of Hyouken no Majutsushi ga Sekai wo Suberu.","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":61153,"title":"Tensei shita Daiseijo wa, Seijo de Aru Koto wo Hitakakusu","title_english":"A Tale of the Secret Saint","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1454/156338l.jpg","synopsis":"Fia always dreamed of becoming a knight. Born into a family of knights, she's the least talented among them, but she still clutches to her hope and trains with everything she has. When the day comes for her to slay a small demon and prove her worth, she ends up face to face with a dragon instead! A deadly injury makes her life flash before her eyes... and she suddenly remembers her former life, when she was a powerful Saint in a bygone era who defeated the Demon King. That life ended in pain because of who she was, making her fear ever becoming a Saint again. Now that the magic from her previous life has been rekindled, she may become a more powerful knight than she ever dreamed–if only she can survive long enough!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":59204,"title":"Magic Knight Rayearth (2026)","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1349/156364l.jpg","synopsis":"New anime project for Magic Knight Rayearth to celebrate the anime's 30th anniversary.","streaming":[{"name":"YouTube","url":"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLVs8KIyueUjWQEJ83sa8kpo4jIjWh_aWT"}],"type":"TV"},{"id":54344,"title":"Mahou Shoujo Ikusei Keikaku: Restart","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1711/152746l.jpg","synopsis":"The deadly game is back!\n\nOnce again, sixteen Magical Girls have been assembled for a high-stakes challenge. Every three days, their Magical Phone pulls them into an RPG-like simulation where they have to work together to fight enemies, solve puzzles, and earn Magical Candy to advance. A staggering ten billion yen reward awaits them at the end—but only for the players who land the finishing blow. With such a tantalizing prize on the line, it's only a matter of time before the girls turn on each other—and if their hit points drop to zero, a game over will be the least of their worries... \n\n(Source: Mahou Shoujo Ikusei Keikaku Wiki, edited)","streaming":[{"name":"YouTube","url":"https://www.youtube.com/@mahoiku2official"}],"type":"TV"},{"id":63098,"title":"Psyren","title_english":"Psyren","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1698/156325l.jpg","synopsis":"Ageha Yoshina is a self-confident high school student who helps others for a fee. On his way back from a job, he finds a strange calling card with the word \"Psyren\" imprinted left behind in a phone booth and decides to keep it, unaware of its purpose. The very next day, Ageha discovers that his classmate Sakurako Amamiya has the exact same calling card in her possession. When he questions her, Sakurako asks him to save her, signaling the day his troubles begin.\n\nConfused by the circumstances of this encounter, Ageha realizes something is wrong when Sakurako goes missing. In an attempt to figure out what is happening, he decides to call the number provided on the calling card and is asked a series of questions by a mysterious voice, ending with a final, cryptic question: \"Would you like to go to Psyren?\" Thus begins two teenagers' participation in a game of life or death within a strange world inhabited by monsters called Taboo. Granted the ability to use psychic powers known as PSI, the duo fight to return to the place they call home.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":61014,"title":"Toaru Anbu no Item","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1459/155570l.jpg","synopsis":"In Academy City, where supernatural abilities are part of everyday science, the city's peace is upheld by an unseen force—the dark side. Among the covert operatives is ITEM, a four-member elite unit. With Rikou Takitsubo's tracking abilities, Frenda Seivelun's explosive expertise, Saiai Kinuhata's impenetrable defense, and Shizuri Mugino's overwhelming power as one of Academy City's seven Level 5 espers, they navigate the city's underbelly, taking on secret missions that never make the headlines.\n\nAs their latest assignment unfolds, the team moves with precision, unaware that their actions are setting the stage for a tragedy that will test their bonds of trust, friendship, and survival in the unforgiving darkness of Academy City.\n\n(Source: MAL News)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":63382,"title":"Kyouran Reijou Nia Liston: Byoujaku Reijou ni Tensei shita Kamigoroshi no Bujin no Karei Naru Musouroku","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1116/155161l.jpg","synopsis":"Lying on her deathbed with seemingly no chance at recovery, a young Nia Liston is soon to succumb to her illness. Unable to give up hope, her parents desperately search for a cure in even the most obscure places, leading to the appearance of a hooded man claiming he can help rid Nia of her condition. But rather than curing her, the hooded man transplants the soul of a deceased hero who was undefeated in battle into the girl's frail body.\n\nGiven a second chance at life as Nia, the hero is determined to recover her new body's strength by using a technique known as chi to target and eliminate the illness at its roots. With her enthusiastic hunger for combat having also been carried over, Nia is eager to return to exploring the world. However, the hero's restless soul yearns to find a worthy opponent who can defeat her on the battlefield, sparking chaos wherever Nia may go.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":60948,"title":"Mezametara Saikyou Soubi to Uchuusenmochi Datta node, Ikkodate Mezashite Youhei toshite Jiyuu ni Ikitai","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1334/156252l.jpg","synopsis":"Sato Takahiro was an ordinary office worker and hobbyist gamer until the day he woke up on a spaceship–one that strangely resembled a craft from a favorite space-shooter game. With a decked-out ship, a crew full of babes, and a fantastic universe to explore, he's going to make the most of his good luck and create the life he's always dreamed of!\n\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)","streaming":[{"name":"Crunchyroll","url":"https://www.crunchyroll.com"}],"type":"TV"},{"id":56733,"title":"Magical★Explorer","title_english":"Magical★Explorer","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.mya