/156321l.jpg","synopsis":"Misaki, a university student, feeling the weight of everyday life and uncertain about her future, she longs for adventure and something she can be truly passionate about.\n\nAt the start of the new day on campus, members of the Travel Train Club (commonly known as the Tetsuryo Club) invite Misaki to join them, as she steps into the world of railways, Misaki's heart beats with excitement for the journey that awaits her.\n\n(Source: MAL News)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":62696,"title":"Choujun! Choujou-senpai","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1351/152531l.jpg","synopsis":"In Chinjuku, the city that never sleeps, there is a psychic senior police officer who has powers beyond human comprehension! His name is Meguru Choujou! Along with his judo expert partner Nao Ippongi, this hilarious duo will keep the streets clean by any means necessary!\n\n(Source: MANGA Plus)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":63713,"title":"Junket Bank","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1189/156034l.jpg","synopsis":"Karasu Bank is one of Japan's leading banks, boasting the third-highest operating profits in the country. Akira Mitarai is a young employee in his second year at the bank's central branch. His exceptional math skills allow him to instantly spot accounting errors but also make his day-to-day life incredibly boring.\n\nOne day, Akira is suddenly transferred to the Special Operations Department's \"Appraisal Unit,\" which he is told is a key department within the bank. Suspicious of his transfer and the unfamiliar department, he is told by his new boss that the bank actually operates a massive underground casino, and that the Appraisal Unit is the department responsible for managing this gambling as well as the gamblers who participate in it. But these gamblers are putting more than just their money on the line, with their very lives serving as collateral to play! Higher risk means higher rewards, but at the top level losing is a death sentence.\n\nOverwhelmed and confused by the strange state of the bank's secret casino, Mitarai meets a mysterious, genius gambler, Shin Mafutsu. Enraptured by Shin's ability to see through his opponents' cheating and emerge victorious, Akira decides to enter the world of life-or-death gambling as Shin's bank representative.\n\n(Source: MAL News)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":63712,"title":"Tensei Goblin dakedo Shitsumon Aru?","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1008/156031l.jpg","synopsis":"Office worker Akira Yagami's altruistic nature usually gets him the short end of the stick. When he dies after saving a kid from oncoming traffic...he reincarnates in another world as a goblin?! Normally, goblins only live for seven days, but Akira's newfound powers let him defy the species' normal life span... and are the key to his path to becoming the strongest goblin ever!\n\n(Source: Yen Press)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":63157,"title":"Keroro Gunsou☆","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1096/154574l.jpg","synopsis":"A new Keroro Gunsou from scratch.","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":64084,"title":"Sekai Saikyou no Majo, Hajimemashita","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1499/157162l.jpg","synopsis":"When Lorna manifests a completely useless ability, she's labeled an embarrassment to her family and kicked out of the house. With no money or food, she's about to hit rock bottom. But then, she figures out how to use