0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1494/153994l.jpg","synopsis":"The internet is full of creepypastas, cryptid sightings, tales of paranormal activity, and unsolved disappearances. These are mostly rumors and pranks fueled by trolls—entertainment. But the unlucky few learn the hard way that some legends are true. Many of these unfortunate souls are doomed, but their luck may change if they cross paths with the boy in the red hood. He roams from town to town and appears wherever strange things occur. Is he a light in the dark? Or living proof that monsters are all too real...?\n\n(Source: Yen Press)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":64326,"title":"Marronnier Oukoku no Shichinin no Kishi","title_english":"The Seven Knights of the Marronnier Kingdom","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1606/158311l.jpg","synopsis":"At the heart of a continent of eight nations lies the Marronnier Kingdom, ruled by the female general Barbaria and her seven remarkable sons, though each of them is different in every way, they share one dream:\n\n\"To someday rescue a princess in a cool way!\"\n\nNow dispatched as envoys to seven foreign lands, the brothers face unknown trials, fated encounters, and a destiny yet to be revealed. A medieval fantasy of romance and adventure—the story begins.\n\n(Source: MAL News)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":63818,"title":"Battle Spirits [Re]: Zekkai no Kuu","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1431/156315l.jpg","synopsis":null,"streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":63938,"title":"Cardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez Unmei Seisen-hen","title_english":null,"episodes":3,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-11-07T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":"2026-11-21T00:00:00+00:00","image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1454/156802l.jpg","synopsis":"Final Arc of Cardfight!! Vanguard: D Series.","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":64344,"title":"Juuou Mujin Dandivine","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1315/158345l.jpg","synopsis":"Twenty years have passed since the combining robot Dandivine defeated the mysterious invaders known as the Aposdoll. With the threat gone, the world has enjoyed a long era of peace. But for toy manufacturer Casga, whose fortunes were built on the popularity of Dandivine merchandise, that peace has come at a cost. Having relied too heavily on the legendary robot's fame, the company has steadily fallen into decline.\n\nDesperate to revive both Dandivine and his struggling business, Casga's president, Genjurou Shijima, dreams of the robot's return—even if it means disrupting the peace. Then, as if in answer to his wish, the Aposdolls suddenly reappear in Tokyo.\n\nAs panic spreads among a population that has known nothing but peace for two decades, high school student Gekiha Shijima is recruited by his uncle, Yuusaku Kuroiwa, the former main pilot of Dandivine. Drawn into the cockpit of the legendary machine, Gekiha finds himself at the center of a new battle.\n\nWhy have the Aposdolls returned after all these years? And can Dandivine rise once again to face the threat? A new chapter in the fight for humanity is about to begin.\n\n(Source: MAL News)","streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":64028,"title":"Tanuki to Kitsune (TV)","title_english":null,"episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1683/157043l.jpg","synopsis":null,"streaming":[],"type":"TV"},{"id":63901,"title":"Sirotan","title_english":"Sirotan","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-10-01T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1247/156572l.j